Origin & Background: Dave Johnson was a talented engineer who became a quadriplegic in a motorcycle accident. Crime Teacher recruited the bitter young man for her Terroid masters. They rebuilt him using “transformable macro-nano technology.” Dave is a Northwestern University grad student and teaching assistant working on his doctoral thesis in electrical engineering. When his powers are inactive, he looks just like (and is as fragile as) a normal human. He activates his powers by an active of will, triggering a series of shifting plates and fluid resevoirs to absorb the synth-flesh covering and extrude the various tubes, pipes, wires and conduits that power his bionic enhancements and fully enable him to use all his abilities.